{
  "name": "Autonomous Cold Email Machine",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Autonomous Cold Email Machine\n\n**Required Credentials**:\n- `APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET`: HMAC key to verify inbound payloads.\n- `BREVO_API_KEY`: Access token for CRM lookups and SMTP delivery.\n- `AISDR_API_KEY`: API token for AI-driven copywriting personalization.\n\n**Environment Variables**:\n- `APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `BREVO_API_KEY` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `AISDR_API_KEY` mapped in your n8n environment.\n\n**Testing Protocol**:\n1. Send a POST payload to the Webhook endpoint with the header `x-apollo-signature` set. Verify signature validation succeeds.\n2. Ensure the CRM deduplication path checks Brevo and branches correctly.\n3. Validate that the sparse update code compiles and only patches empty properties.\n4. Trigger a full run and check the recipient inbox for the AI personalization.\n\n**Upsell Note**:\nNeed this workflow tailored or fully managed? Hire **Automation & RevOps by Alfaz** for custom Done-For-You setups: [whoisalfaz.me/contact/](https://whoisalfaz.me/contact/).",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 640
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-1",
      "name": "Workflow Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.sticky",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        -250
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "cold-email-webhook",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "responseData": "allEntries"
      },
      "id": "webhook-ingest",
      "name": "Webhook Ingest",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const crypto = require('crypto');\nconst headers = $input.item.json.headers;\nconst rawBody = $input.item.json.body; \nconst apolloSignature = headers['x-apollo-signature'];\nconst webhookSecret = process.env.APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE';\n\nif (!apolloSignature) {\n  throw new Error(\"Missing 'x-apollo-signature' header. Request rejected.\");\n}\n\nconst computedSignature = crypto\n  .createHmac('sha256', webhookSecret)\n  .update(JSON.stringify(rawBody))\n  .digest('hex');\n\nconst isSignatureValid = crypto.timingSafeEqual(\n  Buffer.from(apolloSignature, 'utf-8'),\n  Buffer.from(computedSignature, 'utf-8')\n);\n\nif (!isSignatureValid) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      status: \"unauthorized\",\n      message: \"HMAC signature mismatch\"\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    status: \"authorized\",\n    data: rawBody\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "verify-hmac",
      "name": "Verify HMAC",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        350,
